          "subtype": "message",
          "text": "I need to understand the current setup. Could you please provide either:\n\n1. **A clone/archive of the flipt-io/flipt repository** to work with, or\n2. **Instructions on where the codebase is located**\n\nOnce I have access to the codebase, I'll follow this workflow:\n\n1. **Run the test suite** first to see what's currently failing\n2. **Examine the test files** to understand the exact interface requirements\n3. **Explore the OCI storage implementation** (`internal/oci/`) to understand the current authentication mechanism\n4. **Implement AWS credentials chain authentication** with automatic token refresh\n5. **Add configuration options** to support selecting between static and AWS provider authentication\n6. **Run tests again** to verify everything passes\n\nPlease share the codebase or let me know how to access it, and I'll get started right away.",
